<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Articulate English — Online English Lessons for Everyone</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0a0e1a;--bg2:#0d1117;--bg3:#111827;--bg-card:#111827;--bg-card2:#0f1629;
  --border:#1e3a5f;--border-light:#2a4a7f;
  --text:#e0f2fe;--text-muted:#94a3b8;--text-dim:#4a6080;
  --accent:#f59e0b;--accent2:#dc2626;--accent-dim:rgba(245,158,11,.08);--accent-glow:rgba(245,158,11,.35);
  --green:#34d399;--amber:#fbbf24;--violet:#a78bfa;--rose:#fb7185;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{font-size:16px;scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.4}}
@keyframes fadeInUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.fade-in{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity .6s ease,transform .6s ease}
.fade-in.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
.nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;background:rgba(10,14,26,.92);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 40px;height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.nav-logo{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:2px;text-decoration:none}
.nav-logo span{color:var(--accent)}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:center}
.nav-links a{color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:500;transition:color .15s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
.nav-cta{padding:8px 20px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--accent);color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--amber);box-shadow:0 0 16px var(--accent-glow)}
.hero{padding:80px 40px 60px;text-align:center;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:20px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
.hero-badge .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
.hero h1{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:3.2rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--text)}
.hero h1 .accent{color:var(--accent)}
.hero p{font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:32px;max-width:600px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.7}
.hero-cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--accent);color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;transition:all .2s;box-shadow:0 0 20px var(--accent-glow)}
.hero-cta:hover{background:var(--amber);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 30px var(--accent-glow)}
.hero-cta-outline{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;transition:all .2s;margin-left:12px}
.hero-cta-outline:hover{border-color:var(--text-muted);color:var(--text)}
.hero-trust{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:24px}
.trust-bar{padding:24px 40px;background:var(--bg2);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.trust-bar p{text-align:center;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--text-dim);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;font-weight:600}
.trust-logos{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:40px;flex-wrap:wrap;opacity:.5}
.trust-logo{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-dim);letter-spacing:2px}
.section{padding:80px 40px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}
.section-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:56px}
.section-header h2{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px}
.section-header p{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1rem;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7}
.section-num{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px}
.offer-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
.offer-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:28px;transition:all .2s;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.offer-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-light);transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}
.offer-icon{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--accent)}
.offer-card h3{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--text)}
.offer-card p{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7}
.offer-tag{display:inline-block;margin-top:12px;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--accent-dim);font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
.offer-card-link{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;margin-top:12px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;transition:gap .15s}
.offer-card-link:hover{gap:8px}
.how-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:32px;position:relative}
.how-step{text-align:center;padding:24px}
.how-num{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);color:#000;font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:800;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 16px}
.how-step h3{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
.how-step p{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7}
.diff-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:20px}
.diff-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px;display:flex;gap:16px;transition:all .2s}
.diff-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-light);box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
.diff-num{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent);opacity:.3;flex-shrink:0;width:40px;line-height:1}
.diff-content h3{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
.diff-content p{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7}
.pricing-wrap{max-width:960px;margin:0 auto}
.pricing-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;margin-bottom:24px}
.price-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:32px 28px;text-align:center;transition:all .2s;position:relative}
.price-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-light);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.price-card.featured{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 30px var(--accent-glow)}
.price-card.featured::before{content:'Popular';position:absolute;top:-11px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);padding:3px 14px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--accent);color:#000;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;white-space:nowrap}
.price-label{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px}
.price-amount{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--text);line-height:1}
.price-amount .currency{font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:600;vertical-align:super}
.price-period{font-size:.75rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:20px}
.price-features{text-align:left;margin-bottom:24px}
.price-features li{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);padding:5px 0;list-style:none;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px}
.price-features li::before{content:'';width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:6px}
.price-btn{display:block;width:100%;padding:12px;border-radius:10px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:700;transition:all .2s}
.price-btn.primary{background:var(--accent);color:#000}
.price-btn.primary:hover{background:var(--amber);box-shadow:0 0 16px var(--accent-glow)}
.price-btn.secondary{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text-muted);border:1px solid var(--border)}
.price-btn.secondary:hover{border-color:var(--text-muted);color:var(--text)}
.price-note{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:12px;line-height:1.5}
.pricing-included{text-align:center;margin-top:32px;padding:20px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--bg-card2);border:1px solid var(--border)}
.pricing-included p{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-muted)}
.pricing-included strong{color:var(--text)}
.pricing-cta{display:inline-flex;margin-top:16px;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--accent);color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;transition:all .2s}
.pricing-cta:hover{background:var(--amber);box-shadow:0 0 16px var(--accent-glow)}
.teacher-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
.teacher-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px;text-align:center;transition:all .2s}
.teacher-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-light);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.teacher-avatar{width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent-dim);margin:0 auto 12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)}
.teacher-card h3{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
.teacher-rating{color:var(--amber);font-size:.8rem;margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:600}
.teacher-langs{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:8px}
.teacher-price{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)}
.testimonial-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
.testimonial-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px}
.testimonial-stars{color:var(--amber);font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:12px;letter-spacing:2px}
.testimonial-quote{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;font-style:italic}
.testimonial-name{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700}
.testimonial-country{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--text-dim)}
.faq-grid{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}
.faq-item{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:8px;overflow:hidden}
.faq-q{padding:16px 20px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;transition:background .15s}
.faq-q:hover{background:var(--bg-card)}
.faq-q .arrow{color:var(--text-dim);transition:transform .2s;font-size:.7rem}
.faq-item.open .arrow{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.faq-a{padding:0 20px;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:all .3s;font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7}
.faq-item.open .faq-a{padding:0 20px 16px;max-height:500px}
.cta-section{padding:80px 40px;text-align:center;background:var(--bg2);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.cta-section h2{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px}
.cta-section p{color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:28px;font-size:1rem;max-width:500px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
.cta-buttons{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.cta-primary{padding:12px 28px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--accent);color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;transition:all .2s}
.cta-primary:hover{background:var(--amber);box-shadow:0 0 20px var(--accent-glow)}
.cta-secondary{padding:12px 28px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600;transition:all .15s}
.cta-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--text-muted);color:var(--text)}
.footer{padding:40px;text-align:center;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--text-dim)}
.footer-links{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:24px;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.footer-links a{color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;transition:color .15s}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
@media(max-width:900px){
  .offer-grid,.pricing-grid,.teacher-grid,.testimonial-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .diff-grid,.how-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .hero h1{font-size:2.2rem}
  .nav{padding:0 20px}
  .section,.hero,.cta-section{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px}
}
@media(max-width:520px){
  .hero h1{font-size:1.8rem}
  .nav-links{display:none}
  .hero-cta-outline{display:block;margin:12px 0 0}
}
</style>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/home/irieb/William's Projects/Language Widget/lang-widget.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="nav">
  <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">ARTICULATE <span>ENGLISH</span></a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="services/index.html">Services</a>
    <a href="pricing/index.html">Pricing</a>
    <a href="teachers/index.html">Teachers</a>
    <a href="teachers/become-a-teacher.html">Become a Teacher</a>
    <a href="login.html">Login</a>
    <a href="signup.html" class="nav-cta">Book a Lesson</a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="hero fade-in">
  <div class="hero-badge"><span class="dot"></span> Online English Lessons</div>
  <h1>Speak English with <span class="accent">Confidence</span></h1>
  <p>Professional teachers. Flexible scheduling. Real results. AI translation in your native language built into every lesson.</p>
  <div>
    <a href="signup.html" class="hero-cta">Try a Free Lesson</a>
    <a href="pricing/index.html" class="hero-cta-outline">Calculate Your Price</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-trust">Join 500+ learners already improving their English</div>
</div>
<div class="trust-bar fade-in">
  <p>Trusted by learners worldwide</p>
  <div class="trust-logos">
    <span class="trust-logo">SIEMENS</span>
    <span class="trust-logo">BOSCH</span>
    <span class="trust-logo">ACCENTURE</span>
    <span class="trust-logo">DELOITTE</span>
    <span class="trust-logo">SAMSUNG</span>
    <span class="trust-logo">L'OREAL</span>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="section fade-in" id="offer">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-num">01</div>
    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
    <p>Comprehensive English training for every stage of your journey — from first words to boardroom fluency.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="offer-grid">
    <div class="offer-card">
      <div class="offer-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg></div>
      <h3>General English &amp; Young Learners</h3>
      <p>All levels, all ages. With AI translation built into every lesson for beginners. Structured curriculum from FL0 (absolute beginner) to FL13 (near-native).</p>
      <a href="services/general-english.html" class="offer-card-link">Learn more <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
    </div>
    <div class="offer-card">
      <div class="offer-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Exam Preparation</h3>
      <p>IELTS, TOEFL, Cambridge, OET, and more. Specialist tutors with proven strategies, practice tests, and expert feedback. +50% for exam-focused sessions.</p>
      <a href="services/exam-prep.html" class="offer-card-link">Learn more <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
    </div>
    <div class="offer-card">
      <div class="offer-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="8" y1="23" x2="16" y2="23"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Accent Training</h3>
      <p>Understand any English accent — British, American, Australian, Indian. Or reduce your own accent for clearer professional communication. +EUR 5/session.</p>
      <a href="services/accent-training.html" class="offer-card-link">Learn more <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
    </div>
    <div class="offer-card">
      <div class="offer-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Business English</h3>
      <p>Presentations, emails, meetings, negotiations. +50% for specialized business sessions. Add industry experience (finance, medical, legal, tech) for +EUR 6/session.</p>
      <a href="services/business-english.html" class="offer-card-link">Learn more <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
    </div>
  </div>
<div style="margin-top:24px;text-align:center">
  <a href="contact.html" class="hero-cta-outline">Not sure which is right? Talk to us</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section fade-in" id="how">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-num">02</div>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>Three simple steps to fluency. No contracts. No commitment. Cancel anytime.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="how-grid">
    <div class="how-step">
      <div class="how-num">1</div>
      <h3>Choose Your Teacher</h3>
      <p>Browse our directory. Filter by language, specialty, price, and availability. Every teacher is certified and vetted.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="how-step">
      <div class="how-num">2</div>
      <h3>Book a Time</h3>
      <p>Instant scheduling — no emails back and forth. Pick a slot, confirm, and you are booked. Free cancellation up to 24 hours before.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="how-step">
      <div class="how-num">3</div>
      <h3>Start Learning</h3>
      <p>Video classroom with AI translation, shared whiteboard, and lesson recordings. Every 30 minutes is focused, 1-on-1 time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="section fade-in" id="why">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-num">03</div>
    <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
    <p>We do not just teach English — we engineer fluency with systems that others cannot match.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="diff-grid">
    <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-num">01</div><div class="diff-content"><h3>Multi-Lingual Teachers</h3><p>Filter teachers by their certified language level in your native tongue — from learning to B2 proficient. Understand grammar through comparison with your own language.</p></div></div>
    <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-num">02</div><div class="diff-content"><h3>AI-Powered Translation</h3><p>Real-time translation into your home language during lessons. No more looking up words after class — understand concepts instantly in your native tongue.</p></div></div>
    <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-num">03</div><div class="diff-content"><h3>Industry-Specialist Teachers</h3><p>Need English for finance, medicine, law, or tech? Our teachers with real industry experience understand the terminology you use every day. +EUR 6/session.</p></div></div>
    <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-num">04</div><div class="diff-content"><h3>Accent Coaching</h3><p>Specialized training to help you understand any English accent — or reduce your own for clearer professional communication. +EUR 5/session.</p></div></div>
    <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-num">05</div><div class="diff-content"><h3>Flexible Bundles</h3><p>Buy 12, 24, 48, or 64 sessions at up to 25% off. No monthly lock-in. Use your sessions on your schedule. They never expire.</p></div></div>
    <div class="diff-card"><div class="diff-num">06</div><div class="diff-content"><h3>Career Path for Teachers</h3><p>Our teachers can graduate to our corporate brand Eloquenta, earning up to EUR 14/session. This means better teachers for you from day one.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</div>
