<div class="section fade-in" id="faq">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-num">07</div>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-grid">
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">How does the free trial work?<span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></div><div class="faq-a">Book a free 30-minute session with one of our teachers. We will assess your level, discuss your goals, and show you how the platform works. No payment required.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">What is the AI translation widget?<span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></div><div class="faq-a">When a concept cannot be explained in English alone, AI translates key terms into your home language in real-time during the lesson. This is included in every session at no extra cost.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">How do I choose a teacher who speaks my language?<span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></div><div class="faq-a">Use the teacher directory to filter by language level. Choose from Below B1 (learning) to B2 (proficient). Each level has an explanation popup with examples of what the teacher can explain in your language.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">What does B1 or B2 mean for teacher language levels?<span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></div><div class="faq-a">These are CEFR levels. B1 means the teacher can handle main points on familiar matters and explain grammar concepts in your language. B2 means they can explain subtle differences and technical vocabulary. See the full breakdown on the pricing page.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">How do bundles work?<span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></div><div class="faq-a">Buy 12, 24, 48, or 64 sessions upfront and save 10-25%. Sessions never expire. Use them at your own pace. The discount applies to the base rate — premiums are added at full price.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">Can I cancel or reschedule?<span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></div><div class="faq-a">Cancel or reschedule up to 24 hours before your session for a full refund. Late cancellations (less than 24 hours) receive 50%. No-shows are charged the full rate.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">What exams do you prepare for?<span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></div><div class="faq-a">IELTS, TOEFL, Cambridge (B2 First, C1 Advanced), OET, PTE, Duolingo English Test, CELPIP, TOEIC, and more. All major English exams are covered.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">How is Articulate English different from Eloquenta?<span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></div><div class="faq-a">Articulate English is for individual learners. Eloquenta is our corporate B2B brand for companies. Teachers start here and can graduate to Eloquenta for higher pay as they gain experience.</div></div>
  </div>
</div>
